To power the Digital AI Assistant with accurate, real-time, and contextual answers, we need structured, backend-level data that goes beyond whatâ€™s visible on the website.

The AI assistant must respond to queries across Devices, Plans, and Promotions and also handle comparisons, FAQs, and eligibility rules. For this, we require consistent API responses (or JSON/CSV exports) covering the following:

ðŸ”¹ Devices

Device ID, Brand, Model, Category

Release Date, Specs (Screen, Camera, Storage, OS, Chipset)

Available Colors, Variants, Virtual Device Flag

Associated Promotions & Eligible Plans

