Links (overview page, support page), Images/Thumbnails

ðŸ”¹ Promotions

Promotion ID, Title, Category, Sub-Category

Start & End Dates, Status (Active/Expired/Future)

Requirements (new line, port-in, trade-in, etc.)

Payout Type & Value (rebate, credit, discount, free months)

Applicable Plans / Devices / Accessories

SOC Group details if relevant

Links, Assets (banners, thumbnails), Notes

ðŸ”¹ Plans

Plan ID, Name, Price Per Line (1â€“10 lines)

Features: 5G Data, Hotspot, Roaming, Priority Data, Add-ons

Eligibility Rules (business size, prepaid/postpaid, line limits)

Included vs. Not Eligible Conditions

Associated Devices & Promotions

FAQ Metadata per plan


ðŸ”¹ Cross-Relationships & Additional Needs

Deviceâ€“Planâ€“Promotion Mappings (many-to-many eligibility matrix)

Plan Comparison Data (side-by-side features, add-ons, pricing tiers)

Structured FAQs grouped by plan, device, and promotion

Business Rules / Eligibility Logic (minimum lines, trade-in combos, discount stacking)

This information will allow us to:

Avoid misinformation/hallucinations

Provide comparison and eligibility answers instantly

Improve customer experience by delivering contextually correct responses


paths:
  /api/devices:
    get:
      summary: Get all available devices
      responses:
        200:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Device'

  /api/promotions:
    get:
      summary: Get all promotions
      responses:
        200:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Promotion'

  /api/plans:
    get:
      summary: Get all plans
      responses:
        200:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Plan'

components:
  schemas:
    Device:
      type: object
      properties:
        device_id: { type: string }
        brand: { type: string }
        model_name: { type: string }
        release_date: { type: string }
        storage_options: { type: array, items: { type: string } }
        available_promotions: { type: array, items: { type: string } }

    Promotion:
      type: object
      properties:
        promotion_id: { type: string }
        title: { type: string }
        category: { type: string }
        start_date: { type: string }
        end_date: { type: string }
        applicable_plans: { type: array, items: { type: string } }
        applicable_devices: { type: array, items: { type: string } }

    Plan:
      type: object
      properties:
        plan_id: { type: string }
        name: { type: string }
        price_per_line: { type: number }
        included_features: { type: array, items: { type: string } }
        eligible_devices: { type: array, items: { type: string } }
        eligible_promotions: { type: array, items: { type: string } }
